sequenceDiagram
    participant GM as GameManager
    participant TFC as TurnFlowCoordinator
    participant PC as PlayerController
    participant Space as Space/Board

    Note over GM: GameState = PlayerTurn
    GM->>TFC: TurnStartedEvent (playerId)
    GM->>PC: TurnStartedEvent (playerId)
    Note over TFC: Phase = AwaitingRoll
    Note over PC: isMyTurn = true

    PC->>TFC: TurnActionRequest (RollDice)
    TFC->>PC: TurnActionResult (allowed)
    PC->>GM: BooleanEvent (diceRollRequest)
    Note over GM: Phase = RollingDice
    GM->>TFC: DiceRolledEvent
    Note over TFC: Phase = AwaitingMovement

    Note over GM: Movement resolves...
    GM->>TFC: PieceMoveCompletedEvent
    Note over TFC: Phase = AwaitingResolution
    TFC->>PC: ActionResolvedEvent

    Note over Space: Space logic fires
    Space->>PC: PurchaseOwnableRequestEvent OR ChargeOwnershipFeeEvent
    PC->>TFC: TurnActionRequest (BuyProperty / etc)
    TFC->>PC: TurnActionResult (allowed)
    Note over PC: Player resolves space action
    Note over TFC: Phase = Completed, awaitingEndTurn = true

    PC->>TFC: TurnActionRequest (EndTurn)
    TFC->>PC: TurnActionResult (allowed)
    Note over TFC: CompleteTurnFlow()
    TFC->>GM: TurnStartedEvent (nextPlayerId)